text.bundle_jumble.config.title: Bundle Jumble Config
text.bundle_jumble.config.shift_drops_it: Shift right clicking with a filled bundle in your hand will drop all of its content
text.bundle_jumble.config.more_bunnies_d: When two rabbits breed, there is a chance up to 3 more bunnies will spawn
text.bundle_jumble.config.automatic_refi: When your bundle runs out of a specific block, it'll search your inventory for more blocks of the same kind and transfer them to your bundle
text.bundle_jumble.config.refill_searche: When trying to refill bundle, it'll also search in your hotbar
text.bundle_jumble.config.enable_leather:
Allows you to craft the bundle using regular leather in addition to rabbit hide.

Requires world reload!
